      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "yeah no specific times or anything, just straight deliveries. i guess u mean like a heuristic or something? like if i dont use a computer, what's a simple rule of thumb to figure out the route without spending all day on it?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
